  <div class="mission-container">
    <div class="mission-text">
      <h2 class="mission-title">PROJECT SUMMARY</h2>
      <p class="mission-text">
        TrueClimate is an alternative approach to helping the world understand climate change, by translating large and complex environmental datasets into more comprehendable visualizations. This is done by combining user-entered data with real-world datasets from API-sourced data, and then comparing personal impact to the industrial sector of humanity. The goal of this website is to reduce confusion, misunderstanding, and self-guilt by presenting accurate and reliably sourced data in an accessable and engaging format. The purpose of this website is not to inform its users on WHAT to do about climate change, rather it is more of a call for something to be DONE about it.
      </p>
